CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1776767959
OL,3,CSix-year-old boy dies in car crash as
OL,4,Cman arrested
OL,6,FA six-year-old boy has died and a man
OL,7,Fhas been arrested following a car
OL,8,Fcrash.
OL,10,FPolice were called to reports of a
OL,11,Fcollision between a black Infiniti
OL,12,FFX30D and the boy on Anchor Drive, in
OL,13,FEllesmere Port.
OL,15,FFamily members initially tried to take
OL,16,Fthe boy to hospital, but they were met
OL,17,Fby paramedics and police near Whitby
OL,18,FSports and Social Club.
OL,20,FHe was taken to the Countess of
OL,21,FChester Hospital, where he later died.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/3
