PN,39902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1776767959
OL,3,CSix-year-old boy dies in car crash as
OL,4,Cman arrested
OL,6,FA 48-year-old man was arrested on
OL,7,Fsuspicion of causing a death by
OL,8,Fdangerous driving, drug driving, and
OL,9,Fdriving otherwise in accordance with a
OL,10,Flicence, but he has since been
OL,11,Freleased on bail.
OL,13,FCheshire Police is asking for anyone
OL,14,Fwith information or video footage to
OL,15,Fcontact them.
OL,17,FDetective Sergeant Iain Condliffe
OL,18,Fsaid: "This was a tragic incident in
OL,19,Fwhich a young child lost his life, and
OL,20,Fwe are committed to doing all we can
OL,21,Fto establish exactly what took place.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/3
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
