PN,39903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1776767959
OL,3,CSix-year-old boy dies in car crash as
OL,4,Cman arrested
OL,6,F"As part of our investigation, we're
OL,7,Fkeen to hear from anyone who witnessed
OL,8,Fthe initial collision on Anchor Drive,
OL,9,For anyone with any video footage or
OL,10,Fthe incident.
OL,12,F"I'd also like to hear from anyone who
OL,13,Fwas present when the child was later
OL,14,Ftreated near to Whitby Sports and
OL,15,FSocial Club."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/3
